  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And that kind of a-- the childish hope and idealism.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I thought that I will be some kind of an industrialist.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I entered, after I graduated from high school, I entered general mechanic, just the lowest level to learn how to deal with metal, and understand mechanics, and factory, and so on.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I worked in the Budapest telephone factory, which the name telephone factory doesn't give justice to the company's activities, because they were manufacturing movie projectors, railroads, railroad station systems, semaphores, and all these lighting systems, gas pumps and all kind of mechanically-advanced apparatuses.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I was there for a year.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I received a diploma of a-- a-- a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It took me a year because, due to the fact that I went to higher education, this gymnasium degree, I didn't have to do the same thing as many people who were apprenticeship like myself, to learn the trade, had to go to school and their education lasted twice as long or more.",
      "word_count": 53
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I received a diploma of being a mechanic.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But in the meantime, they were expropriating all the private ownership in the city and in the country, because Communism took strong foothold in the Hungarian political life.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Communists didn't permit private ownerships of factories, private ownerships of stores, private ownership of most anything.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "First it was only if you had more than 50 people working for you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then it went down to practically if it was only a family business.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most all of those properties were taken over by the-- by the government.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And that's how my father, again, lost his business.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And his private business, which was again, the hat and wholesale, which developed very nicely after World War II, was the expropriated.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
